reviewText: Bad soft core porn and the woman from Cruz's campaign is hard to find. Misadvertising. Avoid it.
I bought the book because of casting of Amy Lindsay in the movie, but she does not make any appearance in the movie so I cut up the CD and threw it away. This should not happen.
This is just gross and it doesn't have any storyline. No humor, no drama, no suspense. Just naked bodies thrusting and moaning like animals.

Even though this may not be the film of the same name described in IMDB, it's a very watchable, entertaining film in itself. Given four stars for what's in the film, not for its being not the same as in IMDB.
